pageContext.description: Edges are broadly bevelled. the inner lines of the bevels joining one another in a point about half way down the middle of the blade & forming a well marked ridge thence to the top of blade. Hilt plate notched & slightly damaged.
pageContext.patina: Brown patina with metal showing through evenly.
pageContext.publications: Prehistoric Bronzes. 129. No catalogue., Foster Bequest 230. The numbers do not correspond in the catalogue., B.A.V. Trump. P.P.S. 1962 No. 5. p. 98., No. 250
